Apply:
cd /usr/local/plan9/src/cmd/acme
patch text.c < /Users/andrew/src/acme/patch/text.c.*.diff
patch rows.c < /Users/andrew/src/acme/patch/rows.c.*.diff
mk install

Undo:
patch -R text.c < /Users/andrew/src/acme/patch/text.c.*.diff
patch -R rows.c < /Users/andrew/src/acme/patch/rows.c.*.diff

Index:
text.c.1.diff	prevents listing hidden dot files
text.c.2.diff	adds basic cursor movement
text.c.3.diff	adds Cmd+S save/put binding
rows.c.1.diff	adds "Load" command
